data.description: You're going to love this well-maintained custom-built home. This home is 1757 sq ft and it offers 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage and a nice enclosed carpeted patio. The front yard is xeriscape and the backyard has a 10 x 21 workshop with electric and window a/c. There are rain gutters all the way around the home with rain catchment barrels. The open kitchen, dining and living area are great for entertaining guests, family and friends. Tile flooring throughout the house and laminate wood flooring in the bedrooms. The master has a large walk-in closet in the bathroom with a jacuzzi tub for a relaxing soak after a long day. This home is conveniently located to NBISD schools, Walmart, HEB and other key shopping points.
